###############################################################################
#									      #
#   File name	    NMakefile						      #
#									      #
#   Description     An NMake file for making all SysToolLib libs & programs   #
#									      #
#   Notes	    make.bat looks for a default nmake file called NMakeFile. #
#									      #
#   History								      #
#    2016-10-05 JFL jf.larvoire@hpe.com created this file.                    #
